Title: Global gene expression analysis of MGAS10870 serotype of Group A Streptococcus (Streptococcus pyogenes/GAS) in the absence or presence of 125µg/ml human calprotectin protein
Description: The goal was to perform global transcriptome analysis on MGAS10870 serotype to investigate and compare the gene alterations of WT grown in the presence of 125µg/ml human calprotectin protein to WT grown in the absence of 125µg/ml human calprotectin protein
